<P class=MsoNormal 0in auto? mso-margin-top-alt: mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; mso-list: level1 lfo1; tab-stops: list 0pt l0 0.5in; **SMURF**?MARGIN: TEXT-INDENT: -0.25in; .5in;><SPAN Verdana? mso-bidi-font-family: Verdana; **SMURF**?FONT-FAMILY: mso-fareast-font-family:><SPAN Ignore? **SMURF**?mso-list:>1)<SPAN 7pt Roman?? ?Times New **SMURF**?FONT:>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<STRONG>&nbsp; </STRONG></SPAN></SPAN></SPAN><SPAN Verdana? **SMURF**?FONT-FAMILY:><STRONG>Monk mitigation -</STRONG> <FONT color=#ff0000>Currently being evaluated.<SPAN yes? **SMURF**?mso-spacerun:>&nbsp; </SPAN>(</FONT></SPAN><FONT color=#ff0000><SPAN FONT-FAMILY: Verdana? red; **SMURF**?FONT-SIZE: COLOR: 9pt;>These new details have been submitted evaluation)</SPAN><namespace prefix = o ns = "http://www.lithium.com/unique/URI"></SPAN></FONT><SPAN 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: Verdana? **SMURF**?FONT-SIZE:></P>
