<P class=MsoNormal 0in auto? mso-margin-top-alt: mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; mso-list: level1 lfo1; tab-stops: list 0pt l0 0.5in; **SMURF**?MARGIN: TEXT-INDENT: -0.25in; .5in;><SPAN Verdana? mso-bidi-font-family: Verdana; **SMURF**?FONT-FAMILY: mso-fareast-font-family:><SPAN Ignore? **SMURF**?mso-list:>5)<SPAN 7pt Roman?? ?Times New **SMURF**?FONT:>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<STRONG> </STRONG></SPAN></SPAN></SPAN><SPAN Verdana? **SMURF**?FONT-FAMILY:><STRONG>Return Kick AA</STRONG> - <FONT color=#ff0000>Currently being discussed</FONT></SPAN></SPAN></P>
<P class=MsoNormal 0in auto? mso-margin-top-alt: mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; mso-list: level1 lfo1; tab-stops: list 0pt l0 0.5in; **SMURF**?MARGIN: TEXT-INDENT: -0.25in; .5in;><SPAN Verdana? mso-bidi-font-family: Verdana; **SMURF**?FONT-FAMILY: mso-fareast-font-family:><SPAN Ignore? **SMURF**?mso-list:>6)<SPAN 7pt Roman?? ?Times New **SMURF**?FONT:>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </SPAN></SPAN></SPAN><SPAN Verdana? **SMURF**?FONT-FAMILY:><STRONG>Leather armor graphics</STRONG></SPAN> <FONT color=#ff0000>(This item was marked as done.</SPAN> Going to re-submit)</SPAN></FONT></P>
<P class=MsoNormal 0in auto? mso-margin-top-alt: mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; mso-list: level1 lfo1; tab-stops: list 0pt l0 0.5in; **SMURF**?MARGIN: TEXT-INDENT: -0.25in; .5in;><SPAN Verdana? mso-bidi-font-family: Verdana; **SMURF**?FONT-FAMILY: mso-fareast-font-family:><SPAN Ignore? **SMURF**?mso-list:>7)<SPAN 7pt Roman?? ?Times New **SMURF**?FONT:>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </SPAN></SPAN></SPAN><SPAN Verdana? **SMURF**?FONT-FAMILY:><STRONG>Discipline stacking and timer issues.</STRONG>&nbsp; A lot of monks feel throw stone should not be on the same timer as phantom lull and planes walk should not be with healing will.&nbsp; Whirlwind also has a very long reuse timer and its tied to stonestance and earth walk, which are some life saving disciplines while pulling.<SPAN yes? **SMURF**?mso-spacerun:>&nbsp; </SPAN><FONT color=#ff0000>This is a new item, I am sending it along.<SPAN yes? **SMURF**?mso-spacerun:>&nbsp; </SPAN>I hope to have information with the next update in 2 weeks.</FONT></SPAN></P>
<P class=MsoNormal 0in auto? mso-margin-top-alt: mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; mso-list: level1 lfo1; tab-stops: list 0pt l0 0.5in; **SMURF**?MARGIN: TEXT-INDENT: -0.25in; .5in;><SPAN Verdana? mso-bidi-font-family: Verdana; **SMURF**?FONT-FAMILY: mso-fareast-font-family:><SPAN Ignore? **SMURF**?mso-list:>8)<SPAN 7pt Roman?? ?Times New **SMURF**?FONT:>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </SPAN></SPAN></SPAN><SPAN Verdana? **SMURF**?FONT-FAMILY:><STRONG>Monk epic.</STRONG> It has no Endurance on it. The Berserker Epic does. That needs to be fixed. In fact, all MELEE only epics need endurance added. Endurance is, after all, a melee centric concept.<SPAN yes? **SMURF**?mso-spacerun:>&nbsp; </SPAN><FONT color=#ff0000>(Currently being evaluated)</FONT></SPAN></P>
<P class=MsoNormal 0in auto? mso-margin-top-alt: mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; mso-list: level1 lfo1; tab-stops: list 0pt l0 0.5in; **SMURF**?MARGIN: TEXT-INDENT: -0.25in; .5in;><SPAN Verdana? mso-bidi-font-family: Verdana; **SMURF**?FONT-FAMILY: mso-fareast-font-family:><SPAN Ignore? **SMURF**?mso-list:>9)<SPAN 7pt Roman?? ?Times New **SMURF**?FONT:>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </SPAN></SPAN></SPAN><SPAN Verdana? **SMURF**?FONT-FAMILY:><STRONG>Purify Body refresh timer.</STRONG> Purify Soul had its refresh timer reduced many patches ago. Purify Body has not had its refresh timer touched. The cleric and monk version cost the same amount of AA and the same amount of AA to upgrade through the PoP upgrade. The refresh timers should be equal.<SPAN yes? **SMURF**?mso-spacerun:>&nbsp; </SPAN><FONT color=#ff0000>Currently being evaluated</FONT></SPAN></P>
<P class=MsoNormal 0in auto? mso-margin-top-alt: mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; mso-list: level1 lfo1; tab-stops: list 0pt l0 0.5in; **SMURF**?MARGIN: TEXT-INDENT: -0.25in; .5in;><SPAN Verdana? mso-bidi-font-family: Verdana; **SMURF**?FONT-FAMILY: mso-fareast-font-family:><SPAN Ignore? **SMURF**?mso-list:>10)<SPAN 7pt Roman?? ?Times New **SMURF**?FONT:> </SPAN></SPAN></SPAN><SPAN Verdana? **SMURF**?FONT-FAMILY:><SPAN yes? **SMURF**?mso-spacerun:>&nbsp;</SPAN><STRONG>Ranged item stats.</STRONG>&nbsp; Monks have to lose stats while pulling due to losing their range item.&nbsp; Some suggestions have been made of using only the ammo slot to throw from.&nbsp; Putting more monk throw able items in game with good stats with a drop rate which makes them a viable pulling tool instead of a rare stat item.&nbsp; More trade skill items with stats so they can be made and sold.<SPAN yes? **SMURF**?mso-spacerun:>&nbsp; </SPAN><FONT color=#ff0000>This is a new item, I am sending it along.<SPAN yes? **SMURF**?mso-spacerun:>&nbsp; </SPAN>I hope to have information with the next update in 2 weeks.</FONT></SPAN></P>
<P class=MsoNormal 0in auto? mso-margin-top-alt: mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; mso-list: level1 lfo1; tab-stops: list 0pt l0 0.5in; **SMURF**?MARGIN: TEXT-INDENT: -0.25in; .5in;><SPAN Verdana? **SMURF**?FONT-FAMILY:><FONT color=#ff0000></FONT></SPAN>&nbsp;</P>
<P class=MsoNormal 0in auto? mso-margin-top-alt: mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; mso-list: level1 lfo1; tab-stops: list 0pt l0 0.5in; **SMURF**?MARGIN: TEXT-INDENT: -0.25in; .5in;><SPAN Verdana? **SMURF**?FONT-FAMILY:><FONT color=#ffff99>Working on getting the notes for each item 20,000 character limit won't allow me to post them all together.&nbsp; I may not get the notes up until tomorrow but I wanted to get the list to you tonight before I went home.&nbsp; Thanks for your patience guys.</FONT></SPAN></P></DIV><p>Message Edited by Ashlanne on <span class=date_text>07-26-2004</span> <span class=time_text>08:55 PM</span>
