<P class=MsoNormal 0in auto? justify; TEXT-ALIGN: mso-margin-top-alt: mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; 0pt; **Oompa-Loompa**?MARGIN:><SPAN FONT-FAMILY: COLOR: Roman?? New ?Times **Oompa-Loompa**?FONT-SIZE: #cccccc; 12pt;>7)&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <B>Discipline stacking and timer issues.</B>&nbsp; A lot of monks feel throw stone should not be on the same timer as phantom lull and planes walk should not be with healing will.&nbsp; Whirlwind also has a very long reuse timer and its tied to stonestance and earth walk, which are some life saving disciplines while pulling.&nbsp; </SPAN><FONT color=#ff0000><SPAN FONT-FAMILY: red; COLOR: Roman?? New ?Times **Oompa-Loompa**?FONT-SIZE: 12pt;><SPAN FONT-FAMILY: red; COLOR: **SMURF**?FONT-SIZE: Roman?? New ?Times 12pt;><FONT color=#ff0000><SPAN FONT-FAMILY: red; COLOR: Roman?? New ?Times **Oompa-Loompa**?FONT-SIZE: 12pt;><FONT color=#ff0000><SPAN FONT-FAMILY: red; COLOR: **SMURF**?FONT-SIZE: Roman?? New ?Times 12pt;><FONT color=#ff0000>Currently being discussed</FONT></SPAN></FONT></SPAN></FONT></SPAN></SPAN></FONT></P>
