<P class=MsoNormal 0in auto? justify; TEXT-ALIGN: mso-margin-top-alt: mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; 0pt; **Oompa-Loompa**?MARGIN:><SPAN FONT-FAMILY: COLOR: Roman?? New ?Times **Oompa-Loompa**?FONT-SIZE: #cccccc; 12pt;><STRONG>Suggested benifits - </STRONG></SPAN></P>
<UL>
<LI>
<DIV class=MsoNormal 0in auto? justify; TEXT-ALIGN: mso-margin-top-alt: mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; 0pt; **Oompa-Loompa**?MARGIN:><SPAN FONT-FAMILY: COLOR: Roman?? New ?Times **Oompa-Loompa**?FONT-SIZE: #cccccc; 12pt;>Innate increase to runspeed</SPAN></DIV>
<LI>
<DIV class=MsoNormal 0in auto? justify; TEXT-ALIGN: mso-margin-top-alt: mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; 0pt; **Oompa-Loompa**?MARGIN:><SPAN FONT-FAMILY: COLOR: Roman?? New ?Times **Oompa-Loompa**?FONT-SIZE: #cccccc; 12pt;>Avoidance </SPAN></DIV>
<LI>
<DIV class=MsoNormal 0in auto? justify; TEXT-ALIGN: mso-margin-top-alt: mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; 0pt; **Oompa-Loompa**?MARGIN:><SPAN FONT-FAMILY: COLOR: Roman?? New ?Times **Oompa-Loompa**?FONT-SIZE: #cccccc; 12pt;>Attack speed. </SPAN></DIV></LI></UL>
<P class=MsoNormal 0in auto? justify; TEXT-ALIGN: mso-margin-top-alt: mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; 0pt; **Oompa-Loompa**?MARGIN:><SPAN FONT-FAMILY: COLOR: Roman?? New ?Times **Oompa-Loompa**?FONT-SIZE: #cccccc; 12pt;>9)&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <B>Purify Body refresh timer.</B> Purify Soul had its refresh timer reduced many patches ago. Purify Body has not had its refresh timer touched. The cleric and monk version cost the same amount of AA and the same amount of AA to upgrade through the PoP upgrade. The refresh timers should be equal.&nbsp; </SPAN><SPAN FONT-FAMILY: red; COLOR: Roman?? New ?Times **Oompa-Loompa**?FONT-SIZE: 12pt;><FONT color=#ff0000><SPAN FONT-FAMILY: red; COLOR: **SMURF**?FONT-SIZE: Roman?? New ?Times 12pt;><FONT color=#ff0000><SPAN FONT-FAMILY: red; COLOR: Roman?? New ?Times **Oompa-Loompa**?FONT-SIZE: 12pt;><FONT color=#ff0000><SPAN FONT-FAMILY: red; COLOR: **SMURF**?FONT-SIZE: Roman?? New ?Times 12pt;><FONT color=#ff0000><SPAN FONT-FAMILY: red; COLOR: Roman?? New ?Times **Oompa-Loompa**?FONT-SIZE: 12pt;><FONT color=#ff0000><SPAN FONT-FAMILY: red; COLOR: **SMURF**?FONT-SIZE: Roman?? New ?Times 12pt;><FONT color=#ff0000>Currently being discussed</FONT></SPAN></FONT></SPAN></FONT></SPAN></FONT></SPAN></FONT></SPAN></FONT></SPAN></P>
