<P class=MsoNormal 0in 0pt; auto? mso-margin-top-alt: mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; TEXT-ALIGN: justify; **Oompa-Loompa**?MARGIN:><SPAN COLOR: FONT-FAMILY: #cccccc; **Oompa-Loompa**?FONT-SIZE: New ?Times 12pt; Roman??>9)&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <B>Purify Body refresh timer.</B> Purify Soul had its refresh timer reduced many patches ago. Purify Body has not had its refresh timer touched. The cleric and monk version cost the same amount of AA and the same amount of AA to upgrade through the PoP upgrade. The refresh timers should be equal.&nbsp; </SPAN><SPAN COLOR: FONT-FAMILY: **Oompa-Loompa**?FONT-SIZE: New ?Times 12pt; Roman?? red;><FONT color=#ff0000><SPAN COLOR: FONT-FAMILY: **SMURF**?FONT-SIZE: New ?Times 12pt; Roman?? red;><FONT color=#ff0000><SPAN COLOR: FONT-FAMILY: **Oompa-Loompa**?FONT-SIZE: New ?Times 12pt; Roman?? red;><FONT color=#ff0000><SPAN COLOR: FONT-FAMILY: **SMURF**?FONT-SIZE: New ?Times 12pt; Roman?? red;><FONT color=#ff0000><SPAN COLOR: FONT-FAMILY: **Oompa-Loompa**?FONT-SIZE: New ?Times 12pt; Roman?? red;><FONT color=#ff0000><SPAN COLOR: FONT-FAMILY: **SMURF**?FONT-SIZE: New ?Times 12pt; Roman?? red;><FONT color=#ff0000>Currently being discussed</FONT></SPAN></FONT></SPAN></FONT></SPAN></FONT></SPAN></FONT></SPAN></FONT></SPAN></P>
<P class=MsoNormal 0in 0pt; auto? mso-margin-top-alt: mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; TEXT-ALIGN: justify; **Oompa-Loompa**?MARGIN:><SPAN COLOR: FONT-FAMILY: #cccccc; **Oompa-Loompa**?FONT-SIZE: New ?Times 12pt; Roman??>10) &nbsp;<B>Ranged item stats.</B>&nbsp; Monks have to lose stats while pulling due to losing their range item.&nbsp; Some suggestions have been made of using only the ammo slot to throw from.&nbsp; Putting more monk throw able items in game with good stats with a drop rate which makes them a viable pulling tool instead of a rare stat item.&nbsp; More trade skill items with stats so they can be made and sold.&nbsp; </SPAN><FONT color=#ff0000><SPAN COLOR: FONT-FAMILY: **Oompa-Loompa**?FONT-SIZE: New ?Times 12pt; Roman?? red;><SPAN COLOR: FONT-FAMILY: **SMURF**?FONT-SIZE: New ?Times 12pt; Roman?? red;><FONT color=#ff0000><SPAN COLOR: FONT-FAMILY: **Oompa-Loompa**?FONT-SIZE: New ?Times 12pt; Roman?? red;><FONT color=#ff0000><SPAN COLOR: FONT-FAMILY: **SMURF**?FONT-SIZE: New ?Times 12pt; Roman?? red;><FONT color=#ff0000><SPAN COLOR: FONT-FAMILY: **Oompa-Loompa**?FONT-SIZE: New ?Times 12pt; Roman?? red;><FONT color=#ff0000><SPAN COLOR: FONT-FAMILY: **SMURF**?FONT-SIZE: New ?Times 12pt; Roman?? red;><FONT color=#ff0000>This is a revised item.&nbsp; Passing the new information along.</FONT></SPAN></FONT></SPAN></FONT></SPAN></FONT></SPAN></FONT></SPAN></SPAN></FONT></P>
<P class=MsoNormal 0in 0pt; auto? mso-margin-top-alt: mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; TEXT-ALIGN: justify; **Oompa-Loompa**?MARGIN:><SPAN COLOR: FONT-FAMILY: **Oompa-Loompa**?FONT-SIZE: New ?Times 12pt; Roman?? red;><SPAN COLOR: FONT-FAMILY: **SMURF**?FONT-SIZE: New ?Times 12pt; Roman?? red;><SPAN COLOR: FONT-FAMILY: **Oompa-Loompa**?FONT-SIZE: New ?Times 12pt; Roman?? red;><SPAN COLOR: FONT-FAMILY: **SMURF**?FONT-SIZE: New ?Times 12pt; Roman?? red;><SPAN COLOR: FONT-FAMILY: **Oompa-Loompa**?FONT-SIZE: New ?Times 12pt; Roman?? red;><SPAN COLOR: FONT-FAMILY: **SMURF**?FONT-SIZE: New ?Times 12pt; Roman?? red;>Propose Solution: To<SPAN>insure that the ammo slot is used as the primary sorce of expendeture of thrown items.&nbsp; With this, place throwing weapons in the game with appropriate stats to be used in the range slot.&nbsp; The ammo should not have to be the same as the thrown weapon and the highest range should be used for distance.&nbsp; These items used for stats should be no-drop and level required to prevent tweeking.</SPAN></P></SPAN></SPAN></SPAN></SPAN></SPAN></SPAN></SPAN></DIV></DIV>
								<p><div style="width: 100%; height: 120; overflow: hidden;">
								
