<P class=MsoNormal 0in TEXT-ALIGN: 0pt; auto? justify; mso-margin-top-alt: mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; **Oompa-Loompa**?MARGIN:><SPAN FONT-FAMILY: red; New ?Times Roman?? COLOR: **Oompa-Loompa**?FONT-SIZE: 12pt;></SPAN><SPAN FONT-FAMILY: New ?Times Roman?? COLOR: **Oompa-Loompa**?FONT-SIZE: 12pt; #cccccc;>5)&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<B> Return Kick AA</B> - </SPAN><SPAN FONT-FAMILY: red; New ?Times Roman?? COLOR: **Oompa-Loompa**?FONT-SIZE: 12pt;><FONT color=#ff0000><SPAN FONT-FAMILY: red; New ?Times Roman?? COLOR: **SMURF**?FONT-SIZE: 12pt;><FONT color=#ff0000><STRONG>The issues with Return Kick and double reposit is known by development and we do have plans to fix it.&nbsp; Currently we do not have a time frame on when these AA's will be fixed.</STRONG></FONT></SPAN></FONT></SPAN></P>
