<P class=MsoNormal 0in TEXT-ALIGN: 0pt; auto? justify; mso-margin-top-alt: mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; **Oompa-Loompa**?MARGIN:><SPAN FONT-FAMILY: New ?Times Roman?? COLOR: **Oompa-Loompa**?FONT-SIZE: 12pt; #cccccc;>9)&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <STRONG>Innate increase in avoidance</STRONG> - <FONT color=#ff0000><STRONG>New item</STRONG>, I would like some more details on this issue, I believe Vicero is already working on that.</FONT></SPAN></P>
<P class=MsoNormal 0in TEXT-ALIGN: 0pt; auto? justify; mso-margin-top-alt: mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; **Oompa-Loompa**?MARGIN:><SPAN FONT-FAMILY: New ?Times Roman?? COLOR: **Oompa-Loompa**?FONT-SIZE: 12pt; #cccccc;>10) &nbsp;<B>Ranged item stats.</B>&nbsp; Monks have to lose stats while pulling due to losing their range item.&nbsp; Some suggestions have been made of using only the ammo slot to throw from.&nbsp; Putting more monk throw able items in game with good stats with a drop rate which makes them a viable pulling tool instead of a rare stat item.&nbsp; More trade skill items with stats so they can be made and sold.&nbsp; </SPAN><FONT color=#ff0000><SPAN FONT-FAMILY: red; New ?Times Roman?? COLOR: **Oompa-Loompa**?FONT-SIZE: 12pt;><SPAN FONT-FAMILY: red; New ?Times Roman?? COLOR: **SMURF**?FONT-SIZE: 12pt;><FONT color=#ff0000><SPAN FONT-FAMILY: red; New ?Times Roman?? COLOR: **Oompa-Loompa**?FONT-SIZE: 12pt;><FONT color=#ff0000><SPAN FONT-FAMILY: red; New ?Times Roman?? COLOR: **SMURF**?FONT-SIZE: 12pt;><FONT color=#ff0000><SPAN FONT-FAMILY: red; New ?Times Roman?? COLOR: **Oompa-Loompa**?FONT-SIZE: 12pt;><FONT color=#ff0000><SPAN FONT-FAMILY: red; New ?Times Roman?? COLOR: **SMURF**?FONT-SIZE: 12pt;><FONT color=#ff0000><STRONG>This is a revised item.</STRONG>&nbsp; New information was passed along, no new development feedback.</FONT></SPAN></FONT></SPAN></FONT></SPAN></FONT></SPAN></FONT></SPAN></SPAN></FONT></P>
<P class=MsoNormal 0in TEXT-ALIGN: 0pt; auto? justify; mso-margin-top-alt: mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; **Oompa-Loompa**?MARGIN:><FONT color=#ff0000><SPAN FONT-FAMILY: red; New ?Times Roman?? COLOR: **Oompa-Loompa**?FONT-SIZE: 12pt;><SPAN FONT-FAMILY: red; New ?Times Roman?? COLOR: **SMURF**?FONT-SIZE: 12pt;><FONT color=#ff0000><SPAN FONT-FAMILY: red; New ?Times Roman?? COLOR: **Oompa-Loompa**?FONT-SIZE: 12pt;><FONT color=#ff0000><SPAN FONT-FAMILY: red; New ?Times Roman?? COLOR: **SMURF**?FONT-SIZE: 12pt;><FONT color=#ff0000><SPAN FONT-FAMILY: red; New ?Times Roman?? COLOR: **Oompa-Loompa**?FONT-SIZE: 12pt;><FONT color=#ff0000><SPAN FONT-FAMILY: red; New ?Times Roman?? COLOR: **SMURF**?FONT-SIZE: 12pt;></SPAN></FONT></SPAN></FONT></SPAN></FONT></SPAN></FONT></SPAN></SPAN></FONT><SPAN FONT-FAMILY: red; New ?Times Roman?? COLOR: **Oompa-Loompa**?FONT-SIZE: 12pt;><SPAN FONT-FAMILY: red; New ?Times Roman?? COLOR: **SMURF**?FONT-SIZE: 12pt;><SPAN FONT-FAMILY: red; New ?Times Roman?? COLOR: **Oompa-Loompa**?FONT-SIZE: 12pt;><SPAN FONT-FAMILY: red; New ?Times Roman?? COLOR: **SMURF**?FONT-SIZE: 12pt;><SPAN FONT-FAMILY: red; New ?Times Roman?? COLOR: **Oompa-Loompa**?FONT-SIZE: 12pt;><SPAN FONT-FAMILY: red; New ?Times Roman?? COLOR: **SMURF**?FONT-SIZE: 12pt;>Propose Solution: To <SPAN>insure that the ammo slot is used as the primary sorce of expendeture of thrown items.&nbsp; With this, place throwing weapons in the game with appropriate stats to be used in the range slot.&nbsp; The ammo should not have to be the same as the thrown weapon and the highest range should be used for distance.&nbsp; These items used for stats should be no-drop and level required to prevent tweeking.</SPAN></SPAN></SPAN></SPAN></SPAN></SPAN></SPAN></SPAN></P></DIV>
