<P class=MsoNormal 0in auto? mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; mso-margin-top-alt: 0pt; TEXT-ALIGN: justify; **Oompa-Loompa**?MARGIN:><SPAN New ?Times FONT-FAMILY: 12pt; COLOR: #cccccc; **Oompa-Loompa**?FONT-SIZE: Roman??>10) &nbsp;<B>Ranged item stats.</B>&nbsp; Monks have to lose stats while pulling due to losing their range item.&nbsp; Some suggestions have been made of using only the ammo slot to throw from.&nbsp; Putting more monk throw able items in game with good stats with a drop rate which makes them a viable pulling tool instead of a rare stat item.&nbsp; More trade skill items with stats so they can be made and sold.&nbsp; </SPAN><FONT color=#ff0000><SPAN New ?Times FONT-FAMILY: 12pt; COLOR: red; **Oompa-Loompa**?FONT-SIZE: Roman??><SPAN New ?Times FONT-FAMILY: 12pt; **SMURF**?FONT-SIZE: COLOR: red; Roman??><FONT color=#ff0000><SPAN New ?Times FONT-FAMILY: 12pt; COLOR: red; **Oompa-Loompa**?FONT-SIZE: Roman??><FONT color=#ff0000><SPAN New ?Times FONT-FAMILY: 12pt; **SMURF**?FONT-SIZE: COLOR: red; Roman??><FONT color=#ff0000><SPAN New ?Times FONT-FAMILY: 12pt; COLOR: red; **Oompa-Loompa**?FONT-SIZE: Roman??><FONT color=#ff0000><SPAN New ?Times FONT-FAMILY: 12pt; **SMURF**?FONT-SIZE: COLOR: red; Roman??><FONT color=#ff0000><STRONG><SPAN **SMURF**?COLOR: mso-bidi-font-family: red; Gothic?? ?Century><FONT color=#ff0000>Currently being discussed</FONT></SPAN><BR></STRONG></FONT></SPAN></FONT></SPAN></FONT></SPAN></FONT></SPAN></FONT></SPAN></SPAN></FONT><FONT color=#ff0000><SPAN New ?Times FONT-FAMILY: 12pt; COLOR: red; **Oompa-Loompa**?FONT-SIZE: Roman??><SPAN New ?Times FONT-FAMILY: 12pt; **SMURF**?FONT-SIZE: COLOR: red; Roman??><FONT color=#ff0000><SPAN New ?Times FONT-FAMILY: 12pt; COLOR: red; **Oompa-Loompa**?FONT-SIZE: Roman??><FONT color=#ff0000><SPAN New ?Times FONT-FAMILY: 12pt; **SMURF**?FONT-SIZE: COLOR: red; Roman??><FONT color=#ff0000><SPAN New ?Times FONT-FAMILY: 12pt; COLOR: red; **Oompa-Loompa**?FONT-SIZE: Roman??><FONT color=#ff0000><SPAN New ?Time