<P class=MsoNormal 0in auto? mso-margin-top-alt: mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; 0pt; TEXT-ALIGN: justify; **Oompa-Loompa**?MARGIN:><SPAN FONT-FAMILY: COLOR: **Oompa-Loompa**?FONT-SIZE: #cccccc; Roman?? New ?Times 12pt;>10) &nbsp;<B>Ranged item stats.</B>&nbsp; Monks have to lose stats while pulling due to losing their range item.&nbsp; Some suggestions have been made of using only the ammo slot to throw from.&nbsp; Putting more monk throw able items in game with good stats with a drop rate which makes them a viable pulling tool instead of a rare stat item.&nbsp; More trade skill items with stats so they can be made and sold.&nbsp; </SPAN><FONT color=#ff0000><SPAN FONT-FAMILY: COLOR: **Oompa-Loompa**?FONT-SIZE: Roman?? New ?Times 12pt; red;><SPAN FONT-FAMILY: COLOR: **SMURF**?FONT-SIZE: Roman?? New ?Times 12pt; red;><FONT color=#ff0000><SPAN FONT-FAMILY: COLOR: **Oompa-Loompa**?FONT-SIZE: Roman?? New ?Times 12pt; red;><FONT color=#ff0000><SPAN FONT-FAMILY: COLOR: **SMURF**?FONT-SIZE: Roman?? New ?Times 12pt; red;><FONT color=#ff0000><SPAN FONT-FAMILY: COLOR: **Oompa-Loompa**?FONT-SIZE: Roman?? New ?Times 12pt; red;><FONT color=#ff0000><SPAN FONT-FAMILY: COLOR: **SMURF**?FONT-SIZE: Roman?? New ?Times 12pt; red;><FONT color=#ff0000><STRONG><SPAN red; **SMURF**?COLOR: mso-bidi-font-family: Gothic?? ?Century><FONT color=#ff0000>Currently being discussed</FONT></SPAN><BR></STRONG></FONT></SPAN></FONT></SPAN></FONT></SPAN></FONT></SPAN></FONT></SPAN></SPAN></FONT><FONT color=#ff0000><SPAN FONT-FAMILY: COLOR: **Oompa-Loompa**?FONT-SIZE: Roman?? New ?Times 12pt; red;><SPAN FONT-FAMILY: COLOR: **SMURF**?FONT-SIZE: Roman?? New ?Times 12pt; red;><FONT color=#ff0000><SPAN FONT-FAMILY: COLOR: **Oompa-Loompa**?FONT-SIZE: Roman?? New ?Times 12pt; red;><FONT color=#ff0000><SPAN FONT-FAMILY: COLOR: **SMURF**?FONT-SIZE: Roman?? New ?Times 12pt; red;><FONT color=#ff0000><SPAN FONT-FAMILY: COLOR: **Oompa-Loompa**?FONT-SIZE: Roman?? New ?Times 12pt; red;><FONT color=#ff0000><SPAN FONT-FAMI