<P class=MsoNormal 0pt; auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: mso-margin-top-alt: auto? 0in justify; TEXT-ALIGN: **Oompa-Loompa**?MARGIN:><SPAN **Oompa-Loompa**?FONT-SIZE: COLOR: FONT-FAMILY: 12pt; ?Times New Roman?? red;><SPAN COLOR: FONT-FAMILY: 12pt; ?Times New Roman?? **SMURF**?FONT-SIZE: red;><SPAN **Oompa-Loompa**?FONT-SIZE: COLOR: FONT-FAMILY: 12pt; ?Times New Roman?? red;><SPAN COLOR: FONT-FAMILY: 12pt; ?Times New Roman?? **SMURF**?FONT-SIZE: red;><SPAN **Oompa-Loompa**?FONT-SIZE: COLOR: FONT-FAMILY: 12pt; ?Times New Roman?? red;><SPAN COLOR: FONT-FAMILY: 12pt; ?Times New Roman?? **SMURF**?FONT-SIZE: red;><STRONG><EM>Propose Solution</EM></STRONG>: To <SPAN>insure that the ammo slot is used as the primary sorce of expendeture of thrown items.&nbsp; With this, place throwing weapons in the game with appropriate stats to be used in the range slot.&nbsp; The ammo should not have to be the same as the thrown weapon and the highest range should be used for distance.&nbsp; These items used for stats should be no-drop and level required to prevent tweeking.</SPAN></SPAN></SPAN></SPAN></SPAN></SPAN></SPAN></P></DIV>
