<P class=MsoNormal 0in auto? mso-margin-top-alt: mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; 0pt; **Oompa-Loompa**?MARGIN:></FONT><FONT color=#ff00ff></P></FONT><SPAN FONT-FAMILY: COLOR: ?Times New **Oompa-Loompa**?FONT-SIZE: Roman?? 12pt; red;></SPAN><SPAN FONT-FAMILY: #cccccc; COLOR: ?Times New **Oompa-Loompa**?FONT-SIZE: Roman?? 12pt;>2)<B>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Monk relative DPS -</B> </SPAN><SPAN FONT-FAMILY: COLOR: ?Times New **Oompa-Loompa**?FONT-SIZE: Roman?? 12pt; red;><FONT color=#ff0000><STRONG><FONT color=#ff0000>DPS evaluation for all classes has begun and will be the focus of part #2 of the class Re-Envision process</FONT></STRONG><FONT size=2><O<IMG height="16" width="16" src="/i/smilies/16x16_smiley-tongue.gif" border="0">&gt;</O<IMG height="16" width="16" src="/i/smilies/16x16_smiley-tongue.gif" border="0">&gt;</FONT></FONT></SPAN> 
