<P class=MsoNormal 0in TEXT-ALIGN: 0pt; auto? justify; mso-margin-top-alt: mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; **Oompa-Loompa**?MARGIN:><SPAN FONT-FAMILY: New ?Times Roman?? COLOR: **Oompa-Loompa**?FONT-SIZE: 12pt; #cccccc;>3)&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <B>Monk Itemization -</B></SPAN><SPAN FONT-FAMILY: red; New ?Times Roman?? COLOR: **Oompa-Loompa**?FONT-SIZE: 12pt;> <FONT color=#ff0000><STRONG>Currently being evaluated<FONT size=2></SPAN></FONT></STRONG></FONT></P>
<P class=MsoNormal 0in TEXT-ALIGN: 0pt; auto? justify; mso-margin-top-alt: mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; **Oompa-Loompa**?MARGIN:><SPAN FONT-FAMILY: New ?Times Roman?? COLOR: **Oompa-Loompa**?FONT-SIZE: 12pt; #cccccc;>4)&nbsp;<STRONG>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Innate increase in runspeed - <FONT color=#ff0000><SPAN ?Century Gothic?? mso-bidi-font-family: red; **SMURF**?COLOR:><FONT color=#ff0000>Currently being discussed</FONT></SPAN><BR></FONT></STRONG></SPAN></P>
<P class=MsoNormal 0in TEXT-ALIGN: 0pt; auto? justify; mso-margin-top-alt: mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; **Oompa-Loompa**?MARGIN:><SPAN FONT-FAMILY: New ?Times Roman?? COLOR: **Oompa-Loompa**?FONT-SIZE: 12pt; #cccccc;>There have been several threads on this.&nbsp; It is felt that an increase in runspeed on all levels will improve our pulling capabilities.&nbsp; The numbers that have been thrown around are 10-20% increase.</P></SPAN>
<P class=MsoNormal 0in TEXT-ALIGN: 0pt; auto? justify; mso-margin-top-alt: mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; **Oompa-Loompa**?MARGIN:><SPAN FONT-FAMILY: red; New ?Times Roman?? COLOR: **Oompa-Loompa**?FONT-SIZE: 12pt;></SPAN><SPAN FONT-FAMILY: New ?Times Roman?? COLOR: **Oompa-Loompa**?FONT-SIZE: 12pt; #cccccc;><STRONG>5)&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Reduce mend timer AA - <FONT color=#ff0000>Currently being discussed</FONT></STRONG></SPAN></P><SPAN FONT-FAMILY: New ?Times Roman?? COLOR: **Oompa-Loompa**?FONT-SIZE: 12pt; #cccccc;>
<DIV><EM><STRONG>Suggested Changed - </STRONG></EM></DIV>
<DIV>Hastened Mend: 5 levels cost: 5,5,5,5,5 6% reduction per level.<BR>Mend = 6min refresh = 360 seconds. 6% = 21.6 seconds, 5 x 21.6 = 108 second, total refresh 4:12secs. </DIV>
<DIV>&nbsp;</DIV>
<DIV>It has been discussed that it would be a good idea to split among the levels instead of having to get to level 70 to be able to start working on these.&nbsp; There has been some discussion over cost but no alternatives have been given so as of right now this is what is being proposes.</DIV></SPAN>
<P class=MsoNormal 0in TEXT-ALIGN: 0pt; auto? justify; mso-margin-top-alt: mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; **Oompa-Loompa**?MARGIN:><SPAN FONT-FAMILY: New ?Times Roman?? COLOR: **Oompa-Loompa**?FONT-SIZE: 12pt; #cccccc;>6)&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <B>Leather armor graphics</B> </SPAN><SPAN FONT-FAMILY: red; New ?Times Roman?? COLOR: **Oompa-Loompa**?FONT-SIZE: 12pt;><FONT color=#ff0000><SPAN FONT-FAMILY: red; New ?Times Roman?? COLOR: **SMURF**?FONT-SIZE: 12pt;><FONT color=#ff0000><SPAN FONT-FAMILY: red; New ?Times Roman?? COLOR: **Oompa-Loompa**?FONT-SIZE: 12pt;><FONT color=#ff0000><SPAN FONT-FAMILY: red; New ?Times Roman?? COLOR: **SMURF**?FONT-SIZE: 12pt;><FONT color=#ff0000><STRONG>Currently being discussed</STRONG></FONT></SPAN></FONT></SPAN></FONT></SPAN><O<IMG border="0" height="16" width="16" src="/i/smilies/16x16_smiley-tongue.gif">&gt;</O<IMG border="0" height="16" width="16" src="/i/smilies/16x16_smiley-tongue.gif">&gt;</FONT></SPAN></P>
<P class=MsoNormal 0in TEXT-ALIGN: 0pt; auto? justify; mso-margin-top-alt: mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; **Oompa-Loompa**?MARGIN:><SPAN FONT-FAMILY: New ?Times Roman?? COLOR: **Oompa-Loompa**?FONT-SIZE: 12pt; #cccccc;>7)&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <B>Discipline stacking and timer issues.</B>&nbsp; A lot of monks feel throw stone should not be on the same timer as phantom lull and planes walk should not be with healing will.&nbsp; Whirlwind also has a very long reuse timer and its tied to stonestance and earth walk, which are some life saving disciplines while pulling.&nbsp; </SPAN><FONT color=#ff0000><SPAN FONT-FAMILY: red; New ?Times Roman?? COLOR: **Oompa-Loompa**?FONT-SIZE: 12pt;><SPAN FONT-FAMILY: red; New ?Times Roman?? COLOR: **SMURF**?FONT-SIZE: 12pt;><FONT color=#ff0000><SPAN FONT-FAMILY: red; New ?Times Roman?? COLOR: **Oompa-Loompa**?FONT-SIZE: 12pt;><FONT color=#ff0000><SPAN FONT-FAMILY: red; New ?Times Roman?? COLOR: **SMURF**?FONT-SIZE: 12pt;><FONT color=#ff0000><STRONG>Currently being evaluated.</STRONG></FONT></SPAN></FONT></SPAN></FONT></SPAN></SPAN></FONT></P><SPAN FONT-FAMILY: red; New ?Times Roman?? COLOR: **Oompa-Loompa**?FONT-SIZE: 12pt;><SPAN FONT-FAMILY: red; New ?Times Roman?? COLOR: **SMURF**?FONT-SIZE: 12pt;><SPAN FONT-FAMILY: red; New ?Times Roman?? COLOR: **Oompa-Loompa**?FONT-SIZE: 12pt;><SPAN FONT-FAMILY: red; New ?Times Roman?? COLOR: **SMURF**?FONT-SIZE: 12pt;>
<DIV><EM><STRONG>Suggested Changed - </STRONG></EM></DIV>
<DIV>A solution to the timer issues is to keep them linked however, say when a monk uses whirlwind instead of waiting 40 min for stonestance to come back, it comes back in 4 min as if it was on its regular timer.&nbsp; This will let us use our more power disciplins more often but will still keep it so we cannot chain use the disciplins.</DIV>
<DIV>&nbsp;</DIV>
<DIV>So if&nbsp;whirlwind is used, both it and stone would grey out but stone would refresh as normal.&nbsp; If stone was used&nbsp;they would both grey out but since the quicker timer was the one used both would refresh as they do now.</DIV></SPAN></SPAN></SPAN></SPAN>
<P class=MsoNormal 0in TEXT-ALIGN: 0pt; auto? justify; mso-margin-top-alt: mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; **Oompa-Loompa**?MARGIN:><SPAN FONT-FAMILY: New ?Times Roman?? COLOR: **Oompa-Loompa**?FONT-SIZE: 12pt; #cccccc;><STRONG>8)&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Add more benifits for staying under weight <SPAN ?Century Gothic?? **SMURF**?mso-bidi-font-family:><O<IMG border="0" height="16" width="16" src="/i/smilies/16x16_smiley-tongue.gif">&gt;<FONT color=#ff0000><SPAN ?Century Gothic?? mso-bidi-font-family: red; **SMURF**?COLOR:><SPAN FONT-FAMILY: Verdana? **SMURF**?COLOR: #cccccc;><SPAN>Currently being evaluated</SPAN></SPAN></SPAN></FONT></O<IMG border="0" height="16" width="16" src="/i/smilies/16x16_smiley-tongue.gif">&gt;</SPAN></STRONG><FONT color=#ff0000></P>
<P class=MsoNormal 0in **SMURF**?MARGIN: 0pt 0.5in?></FONT></SPAN><SPAN FONT-FAMILY: New ?Times Roman?? COLOR: **Oompa-Loompa**?FONT-SIZE: 12pt; #cccccc;><STRONG><EM>Suggested benifits -</EM> </STRONG></SPAN></P>
<UL>
<LI>
<DIV class=MsoNormal 0in TEXT-ALIGN: 0pt; auto? justify; mso-margin-top-alt: mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; **Oompa-Loompa**?MARGIN:><SPAN FONT-FAMILY: New ?Times Roman?? COLOR: **Oompa-Loompa**?FONT-SIZE: 12pt; #cccccc;>Innate increase to runspeed</SPAN></DIV>
<LI>
<DIV class=MsoNormal 0in TEXT-ALIGN: 0pt; auto? justify; mso-margin-top-alt: mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; **Oompa-Loompa**?MARGIN:><SPAN FONT-FAMILY: New ?Times Roman?? COLOR: **Oompa-Loompa**?FONT-SIZE: 12pt; #cccccc;>Avoidance </SPAN></DIV>
<LI>
<DIV class=MsoNormal 0in TEXT-ALIGN: 0pt; auto? justify; mso-margin-top-alt: mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; **Oompa-Loompa**?MARGIN:><SPAN FONT-FAMILY: New ?Times Roman?? COLOR: **Oompa-Loompa**?FONT-SIZE: 12pt; #cccccc;>Attack speed. </SPAN></DIV></LI></UL>
<P class=MsoNormal 0in TEXT-ALIGN: 0pt; auto? justify; mso-margin-top-alt: mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; **Oompa-Loompa**?MARGIN:><SPAN FONT-FAMILY: New ?Times Roman?? COLOR: **Oompa-Loompa**?FONT-SIZE: 12pt; #cccccc;>9)&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <STRONG>Innate increase in avoidance</STRONG> - <FONT color=#ff0000><STRONG><SPAN ?Century Gothic?? **SMURF**?mso-bidi-font-family:><O<IMG border="0" height="16" width="16" src="/i/smilies/16x16_smiley-tongue.gif">&gt;<FONT color=#ff0000><SPAN ?Century Gothic?? mso-bidi-font-family: red; **SMURF**?COLOR:><SPAN FONT-FAMILY: Verdana? **SMURF**?COLOR: #cccccc;><SPAN><STRONG>Currently being evaluated</STRONG></SPAN></SPAN></SPAN></FONT></O<IMG border="0" height="16" width="16" src="/i/smilies/16x16_smiley-tongue.gif">&gt;</SPAN></STRONG></FONT></SPAN></P>
<P class=MsoNormal 0in TEXT-ALIGN: 0pt; auto? justify; mso-margin-top-alt: mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; **Oompa-Loompa**?MARGIN:><SPAN FONT-FAMILY: New ?Times Roman?? COLOR: **Oompa-Loompa**?FONT-SIZE: 12pt; #cccccc;>10) &nbsp;<B>Ranged item stats.</B>&nbsp; Monks have to lose stats while pulling due to losing their range item.&nbsp; Some suggestions have been made of using only the ammo slot to throw from.&nbsp; Putting more monk throw able items in game with good stats with a drop rate which makes them a viable pulling tool instead of a rare stat item.&nbsp; More trade skill items with stats so they can be made and sold.&nbsp; </SPAN><FONT color=#ff0000><SPAN FONT-FAMILY: red; New ?Times Roman?? COLOR: **Oompa-Loompa**?FONT-SIZE: 12pt;><SPAN FONT-FAMILY: red; New ?Times Roman?? COLOR: **SMURF**?FONT-SIZE: 12pt;><FONT color=#ff0000><SPAN FONT-FAMILY: red; New ?Times Roman?? COLOR: **Oompa-Loompa**?FONT-SIZE: 12pt;><FONT color=#ff0000><SPAN FONT-FAMILY: red; New ?Times Roman?? COLOR: **SMURF**?FONT-SIZE: 12pt;><FONT color=#ff0000><SPAN FONT-FAMILY: red; New ?Times Roman?? COLOR: **Oompa-Loompa**?FONT-SIZE: 12pt;><FONT color=#ff0000><SPAN FONT-FAMILY: red; New ?Times Roman?? COLOR: **SMURF**?FONT-SIZE: 12pt;><FONT color=#ff0000><STRONG><SPAN ?Century Gothic?? mso-bidi-font-family: red; **SMURF**?COLOR:><FONT color=#ff0000>Currently being discussed</FONT></SPAN><BR></STRONG></FONT></SPAN></FONT></SPAN></FONT></SPAN></FONT></SPAN></FONT></SPAN></SPAN></FONT><FONT color=#ff0000><SPAN FONT-FAMILY: red; New ?Times Roman?? COLOR: **Oompa-Loompa**?FONT-SIZE: 12pt;><SPAN FONT-FAMILY: red; New ?Times Roman?? COLOR: **SMURF**?FONT-SIZE: 12pt;><FONT color=#ff0000><SPAN FONT-FAMILY: red; New ?Times Roman?? COLOR: **Oompa-Loompa**?FONT-SIZE: 12pt;><FONT color=#ff0000><SPAN FONT-FAMILY: red; New ?Times Roman?? COLOR: **SMURF**?FONT-SIZE: 12pt;><FONT color=#ff0000><SPAN FONT-FAMILY: red; New ?Times Roman?? COLOR: **Oompa-Loompa**?FONT-SIZE: 12pt;><FONT color=#ff0000><SPAN FONT-FAMILY: red; New ?Times Roman?? COLOR: **SMURF**?FONT-SIZE: 12pt;></SPAN></FONT></SPAN></FONT></SPAN></FONT></SPAN></FONT></SPAN></SPAN></FONT><SPAN FONT-FAMILY: red; New ?Times Roman?? COLOR: **Oompa-Loompa**?FONT-SIZE: 12pt;><SPAN FONT-FAMILY: red; New ?Times Roman?? COLOR: **SMURF**?FONT-SIZE: 12pt;><SPAN FONT-FAMILY: red; New ?Times Roman?? COLOR: **Oompa-Loompa**?FONT-SIZE: 12pt;><SPAN FONT-FAMILY: red; New ?Times Roman?? COLOR: **SMURF**?FONT-SIZE: 12pt;><SPAN FONT-FAMILY: red; New ?Times Roman?? COLOR: **Oompa-Loompa**?FONT-SIZE: 12pt;><SPAN FONT-FAMILY: red; New ?Times Roman?? COLOR: **SMURF**?FONT-SIZE: 12pt;></SPAN></SPAN></SPAN></SPAN></SPAN></SPAN></P>
<P class=MsoNormal 0in TEXT-ALIGN: 0pt; auto? justify; mso-margin-top-alt: mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; **Oompa-Loompa**?MARGIN:><SPAN FONT-FAMILY: red; New ?Times Roman?? COLOR: **Oompa-Loompa**?FONT-SIZE: 12pt;><SPAN FONT-FAMILY: red; New ?Times Roman?? COLOR: **SMURF**?FONT-SIZE: 12pt;><SPAN FONT-FAMILY: red; New ?Times Roman?? COLOR: **Oompa-Loompa**?FONT-SIZE: 12pt;><SPAN FONT-FAMILY: red; New ?Times Roman?? COLOR: **SMURF**?FONT-SIZE: 12pt;><SPAN FONT-FAMILY: red; New ?Times Roman?? COLOR: **Oompa-Loompa**?FONT-SIZE: 12pt;><SPAN FONT-FAMILY: red; New ?Times Roman?? COLOR: **SMURF**?FONT-SIZE: 12pt;><STRONG><EM>Propose Solution</EM></STRONG>: To <SPAN>insure that the ammo slot is used as the primary sorce of expendeture of thrown items.&nbsp; With this, place throwing weapons in the game with appropriate stats to be used in the range slot.&nbsp; The ammo should not have to be the same as the thrown weapon and the highest range should be used for distance.&nbsp; These items used for stats should be no-drop and level required to prevent tweeking.</SPAN></SPAN></SPAN></SPAN></SPAN></SPAN></SPAN></P></DIV><p>Message Edited by Ashlanne on <span class=date_text>09-07-2005</span> <span class=time_text>12:01 PM</span>
